    <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> We may disclose information if required by law, to comply with a legal process, or to protect our rights, property, or safety.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Data Security</h2>
<p>We are committed to protecting your personal information. We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to safeguard the data we collect, including encryption and secure servers. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

<h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
<p>You have the right to:</p>
<ul>
